{
  "stem": "2004.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I also noticed that the people who looked young and strong, they were told to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I told my friend, I says, look, when we get to that officer, we better look young and strong.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because believe me, I don't think these other people will ever make it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he straightened out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looked him straight in the eye.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to the right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am next.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm straight, look him in the eye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He looks at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To the right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now as soon as we got to the right, there was the welcoming committee there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The welcome committee was the people, the Jews that worked in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were the ones that-- that worked the gas chambers, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were forced to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they-- one of the young fellows that was there, he says, you are the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, you are-- you are the ones that are going to be alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The other ones are going into the ovens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They will never survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now they have taken us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At the time, I knew that the shower that they were taking us were real showers, because they told us, you are the ones that are the-- you're going to stay.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we were well aware of the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't see the inside of it, but we saw the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We saw the smoke coming out from the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So at that time we were-- this was, don't forget, this is-- now we are already in, I think it's August of '43.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or was it 40-- no, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
